name: The Worriers
description: The Worriers - Designed and printed by hand in Melbourne, Australia, in seriously low numbers. Peer Pressure is a side project of Graphic Artist and Designer, Rob Cordiner, aiming to sporadically release interesting, wearable graphics. All Peer Pressure t-shirts use a high quality AAA garment base. AAA garment fit is standard, so if you like a slim fit you may wish to consider ordering a size down. All orders are dispatched within 24 hours of placement.
